X   <font size=+1>F</font>UNCTION <font size=+1>O</font>VERVIEW</A>
X
X<p>
X<A HREF="func-edit.html"><font size=+1>E</font>DIT</A>, 
X<A HREF="func-move.html"><font size=+1>M</font>OVE&<font size=-1>S</font>CROLL</A>, 
X<A HREF="func-file.html"><font size=+1>F</font>ILE  
X   <IMG WIDTH=32 HEIGHT=32 SRC="../graphics/buttons/left.gif" 
X   border=0 align=middle ALT=""></A>  
X<strong><font size=+1>C</font>USTOMISATION  </strong>
X<A HREF="func-help.html">
X   <IMG WIDTH=32 HEIGHT=32 SRC="../graphics/buttons/right.gif" 
X   border=0 align=middle ALT="">
X   <font size=+1>H</font>ELP</A>, 
X<A HREF="func-misc.html"><font size=+1>M</font>ISC.</A> 
X
X<HR>
X
X<DL>
X<DT><STRONG><A NAME="preferences">preferences</A></STRONG>
X<P>
X<DD><I>Menu</I>: Options
X<P>
X<DD>Specify preferences.  A dialog is shown to select settings for the following 
Xoptions:
X<UL>
X<LI>Show toolbar:
X<LI>Beep with warnings:
X<li>Save window positions over sessions:
X</UL>
X<P>
X<HR>
X
X<DT><STRONG><A NAME="key-bindings">key-bindings</A></STRONG>
X<P>
X<DD><I>Key</I>: Alt-k
X<DD><I>Menu</I>: Options
X<P>
X<DD>This function starts a dialog which displays a list of all user 
Xfunctions, their key bindings and a short description of the function.<p>
X
XIt also shows the keys or key combinations which call this function 
Xand allows to add or remove key bindings.  
XSee <A HREF="customisation.html#bindings">Key Bindings</a> in the 
XCustomisation section for more details.
X<P>
X<HR>
X
X<DT><STRONG><A NAME="edit-toolbar">edit-toolbar</A></STRONG>
X<P>
X<DD><I>Menu</I>: Options
X<P>
X<DD>Not yet implemented.
X<P>
X<HR>
X
X<DT><STRONG><A NAME="set-fonts">set-fonts</A></STRONG>
X<P>
X<DD><I>Menu</I>: Options
X<P>
X<DD>Not yet implemented.
X<P>
X<HR>
X
X<DT><STRONG><A NAME="set-colours">set-colours</A></STRONG>
X<P>
X<DD><I>Menu</I>: Options
X<P>
X<DD>Not yet implemented.
X</DL>
X<HR>
X
X<A HREF="func-edit.html"><font size=+1>E</font>DIT</A>, 
X<A HREF="func-move.html"><font size=+1>M</font>OVE&<font size=-1>S</font>CROLL</A>, 
X<A HREF="func-file.html"><font size=+1>F</font>ILE  
X   <IMG WIDTH=32 HEIGHT=32 SRC="../graphics/buttons/left.gif" 
X   border=0 align=middle ALT=""></A>  
X<strong><font size=+1>C</font>USTOMISATION  </strong>
X<A HREF="func-help.html">
X   <IMG WIDTH=32 HEIGHT=32 SRC="../graphics/buttons/right.gif" 
