X
X<A HREF="function-group.html">
X   <IMG WIDTH=32 HEIGHT=32 SRC="../graphics/buttons/back.gif" 
X   border=0 align=middle ALT="">
X   <font size=+1>F</font>UNCTION <font size=+1>O</font>VERVIEW</A>
X
X<p>
X<A HREF="func-edit.html"><font size=+1>E</font>DIT  
X   <IMG WIDTH=32 HEIGHT=32 SRC="../graphics/buttons/left.gif" 
X   border=0 align=middle ALT=""></A> 
X<strong><font size=+1>M</font>OVE&<font size=-1>S</font>CROLL </strong>
X<A HREF="func-file.html">
X   <IMG WIDTH=32 HEIGHT=32 SRC="../graphics/buttons/right.gif" 
X   border=0 align=middle ALT="">
X   <font size=+1>F</font>ILE</A>  
X<A HREF="func-custom.html"><font size=+1>C</font>USTOMISATION</A>,  
X<A HREF="func-help.html"><font size=+1>H</font>ELP</A>, 
X<A HREF="func-misc.html"><font size=+1>M</font>ISC.</A> 
X
X<HR>
X
X
X<DL>
X<DT><STRONG><A NAME="forward-char">forward-char</A></STRONG>
X<P>
X<DD><I>Key</I>: Right
X<P>
X<DD>Move the cursor one character forward.
X<P>
X<HR>
X
X<DT><STRONG><A NAME="backward-char">backward-char</A></STRONG>
X<P>
X<DD><I>Key</I>: Left
X<P>
X<DD>Move the curser one character back.
X<P>
X<HR>
X
X<DT><STRONG><A NAME="forward-word">forward-word</A></STRONG>
X<P>
X<DD><I>Key</I>: Alt-Right
X<P>
X<DD>Move the cursor one word forward.
X<P>
X<HR>
X
X<DT><STRONG><A NAME="backward-word">backward-word</A></STRONG>
X<P>
X<DD><I>Key</I>:  Alt-Left
X<P>
X<DD>Move the cursor one word back.
X<P>
X<HR>
X
X<DT><STRONG><A NAME="end-of-line">end-of-line</A></STRONG>
X<P>
X<DD><I>Key</I>: Shift-Right
X<P>
X<DD>Move the cursor to the end of the current line.
X<P>
X<HR>
X
X<DT><STRONG><A NAME="beginning-of-line">beginning-of-line</A></STRONG>
X<P>
X<DD><I>Key</I>: Shift-Left
X<P>
X<DD>Move the cursor to the beginning of the current line.
X<P>
X<HR>
X
X<DT><STRONG><A NAME="next-line">next-line</A></STRONG>
X<P>
X<DD><I>Key</I>: Down
X<P>
X<DD>Move cursor down into next text line.
X<P>
X<HR>
X
X<DT><STRONG><A NAME="previous-line">previous-line</A></STRONG>
X<P>
X<DD><I>Key</I>: Up
X<P>
X<DD>Move cursor up into previous text line.
X<P>
X<HR>
X
X<DT><STRONG><A NAME="scroll-line-down">scroll-line-down</A></STRONG>
X<P>
X<DD><I>Key</I>: Shift-Down
X<P>
X<DD>Scroll view window one line down (text scrolls up).  The same effect is achieved 
Xby clicking on the scrollbar down arrow.
X<P>
X<HR>
X
X<DT><STRONG><A NAME="scroll-line-up">scroll-line-up</A></STRONG>
X<P>
X<DD><I>Key</I>: Shift-Up
X<P>
X<DD>Scroll view window one line up (text scrolls down).  The same effect is achieved 
Xby clicking on the scrollbar up arrow.
X<P>
X<HR>
X
X<DT><STRONG><A NAME="scroll-half-page-down">scroll-half-page-down</A></STRONG>
X<P>
X<DD><I>Key</I>: Shift-Alt-Down
X<P>
X<DD>Scroll view window half a page down (text scrolls up).
X<P>
X<HR>
X
X<DT><STRONG><A NAME="scroll-half-page-up">scroll-half-page-up</A></STRONG>
X<P>
X<DD><I>Key</I>: Shift-Alt-Up
X<P>
X<DD>Scroll view window half a page up (text scrolls down).
X<P>
X<HR>
X
X<DT><STRONG><A NAME="previous-page">previous-page</A></STRONG>
X<P>
X<DD><I>Key</I>: Page Up, Alt-Up
X<P>
X<DD>Move view window to previous page of text.  The original two lines at the top of 
Xthe screen are shown at the bottom of the screen.  A similar effect is achieved by 
Xclicking into the scrollbar above the scroll handle.  This function takes the cursor with 
Xit, leaving it always in the current view.  Changing the view with the scrollbar leaves 
Xthe cursor unaffected.
X<P>
X<HR>
X
X<DT><STRONG><A NAME="next-page">next-page</A></STRONG>
X<P>
X<DD><I>Keys</I>: Page Down, Alt-Down
X<P>
X<DD>Move view window to next page of text.  The original two lines at the bottom of 
Xthe screen are shown at the top of the screen.  A similar effect is achieved by clicking 
Xinto the scrollbar below the scroll handle.  This function takes the cursor with it, 
Xleaving it always in the current view.  Changing the view with the scrollbar leaves the 
Xcursor unaffected.
X<P>
X<HR>
X
X<DT><STRONG><A NAME="beginning-of-text">beginning-of-text</A></STRONG>
X<P>
X<DD><I>Key</I>: Home, Shift-Ctrl-Up
X<P>
X<DD>Move the cursor and the view window to the beginning of the text.
X<P>
X<HR>
X
X<DT><STRONG><A NAME="end-of-text">end-of-text</A></STRONG>
X<P>
X<DD><I>Key</I>: End, Shift-Ctrl-Down
X<P>
X<DD>Move cursor and the view window to the end of the text.
X<P>
X<HR>
X
X<DT><STRONG><A NAME="swap-cursor-mark">swap-cursor-mark</A></STRONG>
X<P>
X<DD><I>Key</I>: Ctrl-x
X<P>
X<DD>Swaps the cursor and the mark.  Redisplay the screen if necessary.
X</DL>
X<HR>
X
X<A HREF="func-edit.html"><font size=+1>E</font>DIT  
X   <IMG WIDTH=32 HEIGHT=32 SRC="../graphics/buttons/left.gif" 
