X<html>
X<head>
X<title>Red: Function List Alphabetical</title>
X<link rev="made" href="mailto:mik@cs.su.oz.au">
X</head>
X
X<body bgcolor=white>
X
X<center>
X<table>
X<tr>
X	<td valign=top> <IMG SRC="red-logo.GIF" ALT="RED" > </td>
X	<td> <font size=+3>Function List Alphabetical</font> </td>
X</tr>
X</table>
X</center>
X
X<hr>
X
X<table cellpadding=10>
X<td width=30% valign=top>
X  <IMG SRC="../graphics/balls/orange.gif"><A HREF="func-move.html#backward-char">backward-char</A><br>
